=head1 TEST PROCEDURE

=begin html
<PRE>
                    
       HA0    NUTX      R1      R2     CN0
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | <---- |       |       | 1.Router Advertisement
        |       |       |       |       |
        |       | ----> |       |       | 2.Neighbor Solicitation (DAD)
        |       |       |       |       | 3.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 4.Neighbor Solicitation (NUD)
        |       |       |       |       | 5.(no reply)
        |       |       |       |       |
        | <---- |       |       |       | 6.Binding Update (*1)
        | ----> |       |       |       | 7.Binding Acknowledgement
        |       |       |       |       |
                    
        1. Send Router Advertisement. (R1 -> R1_allnode_multi)
        2. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (DAD). (Unspecified -> solicited-node multicast)
        3. (no reply)
            # Wait during 1 second.
        4. Receive Neighbor Solicitation (NUD). (NUT0 -> HA0)
        5. (no reply)
            # Wait during a maximum of 3 seconds(RFC2461).
        6. Receive Binding Update. (NUTX -> HA0)
        7. Send Binding Acknowledgement. (HA0 -> NUTX)
                    
    Focus Packet Format:
        <A HREF="../images/Binding_Update_message_format_from_MN_to_HA_ESP.gif">6. Binding Update</A>
</PRE>

=end html

=head1 JUDGEMENT

=begin html
<PRE>
 (*1) PASS: HA0 receives Binding Update.
            Then, check whether this packet fills all of the following.
             - Home Address destination option is set to a static address.
</PRE>

=end html

